Breyer Capital's Investments Are Deeply Personal








We are extraordinarily long-term investors and partners. We have deep passion for social media, entertainment/media, digital health, and financial technologies and care deeply about how artificial intelligence, machine learning, and virtual reality will come to redefine and transform all of these unique spaces.
